# About dataset

## Data source
This dataset is from [Forbes AI 50 2022](https://www.forbes.com/lists/ai50/?sh=6702a2aa290f)

## Features

1. NAME => Name of the company
2. INDUSTRY => which can be one of the following industry type: AI infrastructure, Agriculture, Biotech, Construction, Consumer Technology, Customer Service, Cybersecurity, Data Science, Education, Employee Support, Environment and Energy, Financial Services, Healthcare, Media and entertainment, Pharmaceutical, Retail, Sales and Marketing and Transportation and Logistics.
3. FUNDING => among of funding in Millions dollars
4. HEADQUARTERS => location of head quarter of the company
5. CEO => name of the CEO of the company
